{% # Spacer v2.0.0 %}

{% comment %}
  Changelog
  - v2.0.0 — replace the px-size interface (`spacer_block_size` / `mobile_spacer_block_size` / `desktop_spacer_block_size` ranges + `breakpoint` select) with a single `size` argument backed by the `spacing` metaobject. Block-size resolves to `var(--spacing-<handle>)`, so the mobile/desktop divide now rides the spacing token's own responsive `@media` branch (fixed 48rem breakpoint) instead of per-block px + a configurable breakpoint. Same contract (responsive vertical spacer); new interface. Breaking: removed params/settings — re-pick size as a spacing token. `background_color` unchanged. Modifier emission dropped (no `breakpoint` modifier remains).
  - v1.1.2 — emit `{{ block.shopify_attributes }}` on the root for theme-editor block selection (was missing)
  - v1.1.1 — split the `margin-block: 0` shorthand into separate start/end so margin-block-start can chain block-rhythm vars (`--block-rhythm-mobile`/`--block-rhythm-desktop`) as the inner fallback; margin-block-end stays at 0
  - v1.1.0 — read background color via `var(--color-<handle>)` instead of re-extracting `hex_code.value`; reuses the global theme-color CSS variable
  - v1.0.0 — initial
{% endcomment %}

{% doc %}
  @description
  Renders a vertical spacer whose height is a `spacing` metaobject token (`var(--spacing-<handle>)`) plus an optional background color. The mobile/desktop divide rides the spacing token's own responsive `@media` branch — no per-block breakpoint.

  **Intended scope:** vertical-rhythm block at the section level. Don't place inside a row-direction `group` — the spacer's `inline-size: 100%` will claim the full row and squish siblings. (Inside column-direction containers it works fine.)

  @param {section} [section] - The section object containing the block
  @param {block} [block] - Block object containing the settings
  @param {string} [block_id] - Unique block ID for static renders
  @param {metaobject} [size] - `spacing` metaobject token. Sets the spacer height to `var(--spacing-<handle>)` (mobile/desktop resolved through the token). No height when blank.
  @param {metaobject} [background_color] - `theme_color` metaobject for background. Defaults to transparent.

  @example {% render 'spacer', section: section, block: block %}
{% enddoc %}

{% liquid
  assign size = size | default: block.settings.size | default: ''
  assign background_color = background_color | default: block.settings.background_color | default: ''

  capture base_selector
    render 'utility--base-selector', section: section, block: block, identifier: block_id
  endcapture
  assign base_selector = base_selector | strip
%}

<div class="shopify-block shopify-block--spacer" id="{{ base_selector }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  {% capture dynamic_style %}
    {% if size != blank %}
      --spacer-block-size: var(--spacing-{{ size.system.handle }});
    {% endif %}

    {% if background_color and background_color != blank %}
      --background-color: var(--color-{{ background_color.system.handle }});
    {% endif %}
  {% endcapture %}
  {% render 'utility--dynamic-style', base_selector: base_selector, css_content: dynamic_style %}
</div>

{% stylesheet %}
  @layer components {
    .shopify-block--spacer {
      display: block;
      position: relative;
      inline-size: 100%;
      block-size: var(--spacer-block-size, 0rem);
      margin-block-end: 0;
      margin-inline: auto;
      background-color: var(--background-color, transparent);
    }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}
